The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Liep<U+0101>ja'' {[[Latin language|Latin]]: '' Liepaien(sis)''} is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Liep<U+0101>ja]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Riga|Riga]] in Latvia.

==History==
* May 8, 1937: Established as Diocese of Liep<U+0101>ja from the Archdiocese of Riga

==Leadership==
* [[Bishop]]s of Liep<U+0101>ja (Roman rite)
** Bishop Vilhelms Toms Marija Lapelis, O.P. (since 2001.05.12)
** Bishop [[Arvaldis Andrejs Brumanis]] (1995.12.07 <U+2013> 2001.05.12)
** Bishop [[Janis Bulis]] (1991.05.08 <U+2013> 1995.12.07)
** Bishop [[Peters Strods]] (Apostolic Administrator 1947.07.25 <U+2013> 1960.08.05)
** Bishop [[Antonijs Urb<U+0161>s]] (1938.04.29 <U+2013> 1965.08.11)

